\frac{{\mathrm{\partial} \sigma _{Rz}^2\left( {R,0} \right)}}{{\mathrm{\partial} z}} = \lambda (R)\frac{{\sigma _{RR}^2\left( {R,0} \right) - \sigma _{zz}^2\left( {R,0} \right)}}{R},
