The expression (74) is null for a potential separable in cylindrical coordinates because the term $\frac{{\mathrm{\partial} {\Phi _{{\rm {tot}}}}}}{{\mathrm{\partial} R\mathrm{\partial} {z^2}}} = 0$. In spherical coordinates λ = 1, the relation (73) will be used in the following to describe the tilt of the velocity ellipsoid, obtaining for the DM halo

